These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, rock-climbing
The people have 2 different jobs:  journalist, software-developer
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, lacrosse
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, train
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person driving the train##1
3. the journalist is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Hobby       | rock-climbing       | puzzles |
| Job         | software-developer | journalist  |
| Sport       | lacrosse    | biathlon    |
| Transport   | train       | skateboard      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda
The people have 2 different jobs:  social-worker, fisherman
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: sports, epic
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: water-polo, sailing
1. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
2. the social-worker is on the far left##1
3. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Beverage      | mirinda     | 7up |
| Job           | social-worker | fisherman      |
| Movie-Genre   | epic  | sports      |
| Sport         | water-polo | sailing     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, tea
There 2 different types of food: spinach, blueberry
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, rock
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, airplane
1. the fan of rock is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person drinking juice is the person driving the airplane##1
3. the person eating spinach is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage      | juice | tea  |
| Food          | spinach    | blueberry   |
| Music-Genre   | rock  | disco   |
| Transport     | airplane     | ship |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, lemonade
There 2 different types of food: lettuce, radish
The people have 2 different jobs:  chef, bartender
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: reggae, electronic
1. the fan of reggae is on the far left##1
2. the chef is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is the person eating lettuce##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | coffee       | lemonade |
| Food          | radish         | lettuce    |
| Job           | bartender | chef    |
| Music-Genre   | reggae           | electronic   |

