The people prefer 2 different music-genres: pop, funk
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: lacrosse, cricket
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, motorbike
1. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Hobby         | camping | rock-climbing   |
| Music-Genre   | pop | funk       |
| Sport         | lacrosse   | cricket |
| Transport     | motorbike    | boat     |

