The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, electronic
There are 2 different nationalities: mexican, dutch
2 different pets are kept: cat, dog
1. the dutch is the owner of the dog##1
2. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person eating orange##1
3. the dutch is on the right of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |
| Food          | orange | plum |
| Music-Genre   | r&b     | electronic      |
| Nationality   | mexican | dutch    |
| Pet           | cat    | dog    |

