.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  project-manager, teacher
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: horror, drama
2 different pets are kept: ferret, turtle
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, scooter
1. the project-manager is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
2. the project-manager is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
3. the owner of the ferret is the teacher##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Job           | teacher | project-manager     |
| Movie-Genre   | horror          | drama |
| Pet           | ferret          | turtle    |
| Transport     | scooter            | motorbike       |

 